  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"911\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/npr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=911&amp;height=305\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646545/npr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"343\" data-width=\"1023\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646566\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"npr.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e7628f71-fc22-4d20-aa0d-c5244e12e066\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/npr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1023&amp;height=343 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/npr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=911&amp;height=305 1x\"></span><p /><p>There are 3 required components for setting up a stylized render:</p><p /><h4 id=\"StylizedLooksinHoudiniOverview-1.AddaStylizedDisplayFilter\">1. Add a Stylized Display Filter</h4><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"864\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/stylizedfilters.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=536&amp;height=295\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646545/stylizedfilters.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"295\" data-width=\"536\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646569\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylizedfilters.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ac9aa598-10bc-4ace-9f7a-3ce25022f54e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/stylizedfilters.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=536&amp;height=295 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/stylizedfilters.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=536&amp;height=295 1x\"></span><p /><h4 id=\"StylizedLooksinHoudiniOverview-2.EnableStylizedAOVs\">2. Enable Stylized AOVs</h4><p>The easiest way to enable the AOVs required for Stylized rendering is to create a R26 Stylized ROP from the RenderMan menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_menu.jpg\" width=\"642\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_menu.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=642&amp;height=48\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_menu.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"48\" data-width=\"642\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646560\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_menu.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"646cfe4d-6385-4fe9-bad2-4b41a2215fc6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_menu.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=642&amp;height=48 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_menu.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=642&amp;height=48 1x\"></span><p>This will automatically create a RenderMan ROP and activate all the AOVS needed for rendering in Stylized Looks.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_2.jpg\" width=\"1559\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1559&amp;height=1395\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1414\" data-width=\"1580\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646557\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ec27f09c-2461-41bd-9150-759cf3d9177d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1580&amp;height=1414 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/RenderMan_RfH_StylizedLooks_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1559&amp;height=1395 1x\"></span><p /><p>If you already have a RenderMan ROP node, you can also manually enable the Sylized AOVS under Images → Stylized</p><p /><h4 id=\"StylizedLooksinHoudiniOverview-3.ConnectPxrStylizedControltomaterials\">3. Connect PxrStylizedControl to materials</h4><p>Not all objects in the scene need to have this pattern.  A dynamic array is needed to connect the integer output of PxrStylizedControl to PxrSurface's utilityPattern input. To add PxrStylizedControl to multiple materials, use the Stylize tool found in the RenderMan menu.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"783\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/stylizedpattern.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=536&amp;height=300\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646545/stylizedpattern.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"300\" data-width=\"536\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646572\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylizedpattern.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7cff1118-ca27-4874-abe6-415b1c253f18\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/stylizedpattern.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=536&amp;height=300 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646545/stylizedpattern.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433155560&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=536&amp;height=300 1x\"></span><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"76adfe08-fd74-45c7-8f0b-d636b31f607b\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The &quot;R24 Stylized&quot; shelf button will set up all 3 necessary components described above</p><ul><li><p>Create a RIS ROP with stylized looks enabled.</p></li><li><p>Adds Hatching display filter.</p></li><li><p>Adds PxrStylizedControl to the materials of all selected objects.</p></li></ul></div></div><p />"
    }
  },
